7-29T22:16:49.000Z","msg":"Just do it"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"Ok thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:21:06.000Z","msg":"You're welcome"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"多謝你鼓勵我死  我都覺我呢種人 <br />\n唔應該生存"},{"pid":"d09f5e8761790a6aad41d49c745c3a3fd022d485","tid":760751,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:42:07.000Z","msg":"追女團減壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/064128_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F064128_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dbdc7d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/064134_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F064134_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=c91d3cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"973d2eb512c1a3864242efd9cbc34d1ab313cb6f","tid":760751,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4885599775688828b216f40dd73f5c9c8fbcb759","tid":760751,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32328fb874376ebc8543348fd282a6c08d4b171e","tid":760751,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f146939201a6979db3641fe4499d8723e5436a5b","tid":760751,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"Ok thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:21:06.000Z","msg":"You're welcome"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"多謝你鼓勵我死  我都覺我呢種人 <br />\n唔應該生存"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=JOglu5YfauMX5Jo8bnbi2v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=844011c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至日，下午８時至凌晨１時）即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}